    Return true

Note: Untaint Terraform resource
Process called "terraform_untaint" that takes working_directory as String and resource_address as String returns Boolean:
    Let parameters be list containing
    Add resource_address to parameters
    
    Let result be execute_terraform_command with command as "untaint" and parameters as parameters and working_directory as working_directory
    If not result["success"]:
        Throw create_runtime_error with operation as "terraform_untaint" and context as dictionary with:
